noticias argentinas reported 
earlier hundreds of rebels were forced out of a tank factory 
an infantry base several coast guard buildings and another army 
installation in the fourth uprising by the restive argentine 
military in as many years 
in contrast to three uprisings under thenpresident raul 
alfonsin president carlos menem and army chief gen martin bonnet 
refused to negotiate with rebels who demanded a shakeup of the 
high command and a bigger military budget 
menem in his 16th month of power early monday declared a 
