adequately protect women or fetuses 
i think we anticipated that they would not hear it from a 
practical standpoint it was a good settlement said clinic owner 
dr richard ragsdale of rockford who sued the state to overturn 
regulations he said were unnecessary for abortions before 18 weeks 
