people who killed them connolly said 
most of the murders 57 percent occurred on the street 
almost a quarter 24 percent happened during the commission of 
another crime most often robbery 
the exact date isnt known but the citys homicide rate passed 
the 2000 mark sometime during the last two weeks of november said 
department spokesman sgt peter sweeney 
