</TEXT>
<TEXT>
the daily news has filed a 150 million civil 
racketeering lawsuit against union groups and drivers for allegedly 
conspiring to force the news to either accept wasteful contracts or 
sell the paper to them 
more incidents of violence or threats of violence were reported 
