as the possibility of war looms in the persian 
gulf debate is being renewed over whether the allvolunteer force 
unfairly excuses the elite while the poor and black face the 
fighting and dying some say a draft would be more fair 
fewer families are giving more and more says former 
secretary of the navy james h webb 
