population because so many of them want to be in the military 
gen colin l powell the chairman of the joint chiefs of staff 
who is black told the washington post recently i dont think 
its disproportionate or wrong i think its a choice the american 
people made when they said have a volunteer army and allow those 
who want to serve to serve 
