support of several other nations was expected to offer a proposal 
for removing barriers to trade in financial services he said the 
measure has the support of the united states and the common market 
the uruguay round is the eighth in a series of negotiating 
sessions designed to reduce tariffs and lower barriers to global 
trade the negotiations are sponsored by the general agreement on 
tariffs and trade which was created in 1947 as a forum and an 
agreement to freer world trade 
